ces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屋企好多位可以種野<br />\n一直想種<br />\n但一諗起有蟲我就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f2d9df9e292e14c2d9207af3d1c2d5c0db2e09","tid":171271,"uid":17772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T08:37:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無咩種左係完全唔會有蟲？&amp;唔會惹到蟲<br />\n<br />\n利申勁撚驚蟲 但其實又幾鍾意花花草草 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好比泥土外露太多，鋪dd 沙石係面，因為蟲仔仲意係濕土度產卵。同注意加水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks<br />\n即是無野都唔會有蟲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屋企好多位可以種野<br />\n一直想種<br />\n但一諗起有蟲我就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果同你講100%無就一定呃你，只要注意下衛生，注意積水，問題不大。同埋一開始唔好種太多，一兩盤開始，唔好簡有花住先。好容易打理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己都好怕鹽蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd1bdae3fbfb08c6a89065e9687259385e93d67","tid":171271,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無咩種左係完全唔會有蟲？&amp;唔會惹到蟲<br />\n<br />\n利申勁撚驚蟲 但其實又幾鍾意花花草草 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好比泥土外露太多，鋪dd 沙石係面，因為蟲仔仲意係濕土度產卵。同注意加水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks<br />\n即是無野都唔會有蟲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屋企好多位可以種野<br />\n一直想種<br />\n但一諗起有蟲我就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果同你講100%無就一定呃你，只要注意下衛生，注意積水，問題不大。同埋一開始唔好種太多，一兩盤開始，唔好簡有花住先。好容易打理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己都好怕鹽蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即是花仲多蟲...<br />\n以前問過花農<br />\n佢地過香草勁撚多草<br />\n嚇到我唔夠膽食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以自問連菜都好少食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鹽蛇老鼠小強我都唔驚<br />\n但係蟲就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6b31460397c935d6b92936c1a31b66785d1ed0","tid":171271,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T09:05:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人做呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實依一行好專業<br />\n<br />\n利申：只係屋企花園種下野，算有個花圃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢行好多野要學<br />\n泥土 病蟲害 品種 都有排學<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4d0e7461d1a599d2ad73600407c3fa7d8b5758","tid":171271,"uid":17772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><